{"tid":344620,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Dark souls 1 殺左npc仲有冇得爆機？","createTime":"2017-08-02T11:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T02:17:23.000Z","uid":61962,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"49e17466174febfb06d5b418ea4b63dfd809f515","tid":344620,"uid":61962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T11:46:03.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最重要連鐘樓贖罪果隻都殺埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好後悔貪殺完有野拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家隻激嬲左個洋蔥騎士打唔贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有冇可能玩落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e916bca22c61e2fda56a0920651704ad2fd7c039","tid":344620,"uid":61962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T11:48:28.000Z","msg":"唔想從新開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"570ab60742f50a9dd8666c098e5102d5ff40375d","tid":344620,"uid":61962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T11:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"503283b0465bfdd01fb116a597fb9dc14a8ced82","tid":344620,"uid":608,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T12:08:17.000Z","msg":"殺撚晒都爆到機"},{"pid":"71c2234b613a0ccdcecefff65a1b70ec32b06db4","tid":344620,"uid":61962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T12:15:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>殺撚晒都爆到機</blockquote><br />\n武器果度點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29488249ff85b7dff0fce74f0d69ba5a0c12d750","tid":344620,"uid":61962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T12:46:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.g