,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:52:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁撚易玩都擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a5452f48510f4ad1a8cdda7aaec0e7362fc055","tid":344620,"uid":61523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:57:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁撚易玩都擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係唔難玩, 識去攞勁裝就得"},{"pid":"2ff0bc9a5f4f009904caac545b93d866bd37a878","tid":344620,"uid":61962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T14:03:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁撚易玩都擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係唔難玩, 識去攞勁裝就得</blockquote><br />\n仲用緊射火龍尾拎果把200攻刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6863c40b60728326881e5d2aee1303400c82e6","tid":344620,"uid":34981,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T14:06:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁撚易玩都擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係唔難玩, 識去攞勁裝就得</blockquote><br />\n仲用緊射火龍尾拎果把200攻刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n殺商人攞佢把打刀<br />\n雷質變，可以用到尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1763b2f607854c05083ca29d6aecc0e4b80c8e0c","tid":344620,"uid":61962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T14:34:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁撚易玩都擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係唔難玩, 識去攞勁裝就得</blockquote><br />\n仲用緊射火龍尾拎果把200攻刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n殺商人攞佢把打刀<br />\n雷質變，可以用到尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲教我繼續殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18490680f22b7bbe87cb7ff4ec06800a6c446ec2","tid":344620,"uid":61523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T22:45:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁撚易玩都擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係唔難玩, 識去攞勁裝就得</blockquote><br />\n仲用緊射火龍尾拎果把200攻刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n殺商人攞佢把打刀<br />\n雷質變，可以用到尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲教我繼續殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實真係一見面就殺曬所有可以殺嘅npc都唔難爆機<br />\n<br />\n隻game有四個鐵匠得三個殺倒<br />\n<br />\n果把200攻刀冇用, 又要打成世先囉倒<br />\n<br />\n大不了用Astora's Straight Sword+5都夠<br />\n當然如果好彩有BK/SK系武器就更好啦, BK/SK系武器係基本上NG最高攻嘅武器<br />\n<br />\n如果上面果d你唔夠upgrade materials, 就用Gravelord Sword, 一開始就攞倒, 易upgrade, 打到後期一定上倒+5, 仲要好高攻"},{"pid":"dc8ccd697f3ab69df04a79f5c34365d11793ac7e","tid":344620,"uid":61962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T02:20:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁撚易玩都擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係唔難玩, 識去攞勁裝就得</blockquote><br />\n仲用緊射火龍尾拎果把200攻刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n殺商人攞佢把打刀<br />\n雷質變，可以用到尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲教我繼續殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實真係一見面就殺曬所有可以殺嘅npc都唔難爆機<br />\n<br />\n隻game有四個鐵匠得三個殺倒<br />\n<br />\n果把200攻刀冇用, 又要打成世先囉倒<br />\n<br />\n大不了用Astora's Straight Sword+5都夠<br />\n當然如果好彩有BK/SK系武器就更好啦, BK/SK系武器係基本上NG最高攻嘅武器<br />\n<br />\n如果上面果d你唔夠upgrade materials, 就用Gravelord Sword, 一開始就攞倒, 易upgrade, 打到後期一定上倒+5, 仲要好高攻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鐵匠淨係殺左Andrei<br />\n啱先打先廢村隻蜘蛛boss<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01021f4d5587447d070222e29b190782695c0d0e","tid":344620,"uid":61962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T05:49:05.000Z","msg":"而家打唔贏咬住把劍果隻狼boss<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89547d31a43407c2e6b8c899cfbfb100f5d702bc","tid":344620,"uid":37221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T05:51:54.000Z","msg":"玩魔法流, 入到DLC拎到飛沬已經屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb98e0aa186242599fd31f4d8440430140e6e46","tid":344620,"uid":108878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T05:55:08.000Z","msg":"個人覺得ds1用大盾或者玩法術都係easy mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ac7ac9e2f015bb87a02cc0c5b5d6b1c4d40b21","tid":344620,"uid":61523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:40:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個人覺得ds1用大盾或者玩法術都係easy mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nds1 very easy mode: 法術加重甲<br />\n<br />\nboss打你就食水/人性, 最少打到ng+都仲可以咁玩"},{"pid":"322a89b6304388ca422fa9931543c9317be52225","tid":344620,"uid":61523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:42:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家打唔贏咬住把劍果隻狼boss<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔洗咁早打, 去左anor londo攞左王器先啦"},{"pid":"13026f176e680409e87bc2a5c3a1c7dd963fe633","tid":344620,"uid":61523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:52:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁撚易玩都擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係唔難玩, 識去攞勁裝就得</blockquote><br />\n仲用緊射火龍尾拎果把200攻刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n殺商人攞佢把打刀<br />\n雷質變，可以用到尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲教我繼續殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實真係一見面就殺曬所有可以殺嘅npc都唔難爆機<br />\n<br />\n隻game有四個鐵匠得三個殺倒<br />\n<br />\n果把200攻刀冇用, 又要打成世先囉倒<br />\n<br />\n大不了用Astora's Straight Sword+5都夠<br />\n當然如果好彩有BK/SK系武器就更好啦, BK/SK系武器係基本上NG最高攻嘅武器<br />\n<br />\n如果上面果d你唔夠upgrade materials, 就用Gravelord Sword, 一開始就攞倒, 易upgrade, 打到後期一定上倒+5, 仲要好高攻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鐵匠淨係殺左Andrei<br />\n啱先打先廢村隻蜘蛛boss<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實new londo(小隆德)有一個打唔死(其實應該殺得死, 但係一定唔會係誤殺)嘅鐵匠, 但係可能要細心d搵先搵倒, 再唔係上網查(Rickert of Vinheim)<br />\n<br />\n當然鐵匠中最有用係Andre of Astora, 得佢先整倒+6/+11嘅武器出黎<br />\n<br />\n但係用Demon Titanite/Dragon Scales/Twinkling Titanite upgrade嘅野本身就最多去到+5"},{"pid":"73465c4a0bb11d7f14d7c90a8b40f66a8e851cb2","tid":344620,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T07:26:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁撚易玩都擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係唔難玩, 識去攞勁裝就得</blockquote><br />\n仲用緊射火龍尾拎果把200攻刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n殺商人攞佢把打刀<br />\n雷質變，可以用到尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲教我繼續殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實真係一見面就殺曬所有可以殺嘅npc都唔難爆機<br />\n<br />\n隻game有四個鐵匠得三個殺倒<br />\n<br />\n果把200攻刀冇用, 又要打成世先囉倒<br />\n<br />\n大不了用Astora's Straight Sword+5都夠<br />\n當然如果好彩有BK/SK系武器就更好啦, BK/SK系武器係基本上NG最高攻嘅武器<br />\n<br />\n如果上面果d你唔夠upgrade materials, 就用Gravelord Sword, 一開始就攞倒, 易upgrade, 打到後期一定上倒+5, 仲要好高攻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鐵匠淨係殺左Andrei<br />\n啱先打先廢村隻蜘蛛boss<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實new londo(小隆德)有一個打唔死(其實應該殺得死, 但係一定唔會係誤殺)嘅鐵匠, 但係可能要細心d搵先搵倒, 再唔係上網查(Rickert of Vinheim)<br />\n<br />\n當然鐵匠中最有用係Andre of Astora, 得佢先整倒+6/+11嘅武器出黎<br />\n<br />\n但係用Demon Titanite/Dragon Scales/Twinkling Titanite upgrade嘅野本身就最多去到+5</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://darksouls.wikidot.com/dragon-greatsword\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdarksouls.wikidot.com%2Fdra